{"iti50:0.1":"Itivuttaka 50 ","iti50:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti50:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","iti50:0.4":"Mulasutta ","iti50:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti50:2.1":"“Tinimani, bhikkhave, akusalamulani. ","iti50:2.2":"Katamani tini? ","iti50:2.3":"Lobho akusalamulam, doso akusalamulam, moho akusalamulam—","iti50:2.4":"imani kho, bhikkhave, tini akusalamulani”ti. ","iti50:2.5":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti50:2.6":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti50:3.1":"“Lobho doso ca moho ca, ","iti50:3.2":"purisam papacetasam; ","iti50:3.3":"Himsanti attasambhuta, ","iti50:3.4":"tacasaramva samphalan”ti. ","iti50:4.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti50:4.2":"Pathamam. "}